message: 1、修复部分手机由于没有安装DocumentsUI app，导致生成模块功能闪退||2、模拟按钮适配Material You设计语言||3、优化日志反馈功能||4、完善帮助文档，遇到问题请先查看帮助文档
message_en: 1. Fix that some mobile phones do not have the DocumentsUI app installed, causing the function of generating the magisk module to crash.||2. The simulate button adapts to Material You design language||3. Optimize the log feedback function||4. Improve the help document, please check the help document first if you have any problems.
